The Keiser Report  No. 118
= Max Keiser and Stacy Herbert =
Thursday, 03 February 2011


[sebaygo1]


Silver Stick for JP Vampire!

Max and Stacy talk about French President Nicolas Sarkozy going postal on JP Morgan CEO, Jamie Dimon and about the US Drug Enforcement Agency goes Village People with their big lipped rubber ducky for sale. In the second half of the show, Max talks to Sandeep Jaitly of Bullionbasis.com about a gold standard, backwardization and the Austrian school of economics.
